ioRwDVWas.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152428BvfyDsS5zGo9nERp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191524299XoNnTKC3zDP6ZLf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152429aQOEDjThpFfABke0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152429sJezBvXTolwN27SY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152426np6eCdK2fqo5BzFS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152429zMTKfQxv5o12r9Um.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152429FIQc8b6utZzoJG4r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152429v5FpPrJl87oVS1GH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152430oeMaXp3qQWOP9U0E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152430iMbmUVsFB8wTPOy7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152431b98hfdG0rt6eOaSN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152431YA2npTsWhcUMtyES.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152431OBZ8lKUh5rvfJ9jR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219152431oFVaxYjsdeKbPfin.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191524311w8Y9FhPayO2BpU5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191524314uzRLr0WBMHCsmnS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>伦敦时装周继续。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/london/jw-anderson/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">JW Anderson 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>设计师 JW Anderson 刚在巴黎展示完早秋和男装系列：昏暗房间里的中世纪农夫风格。伦敦时装周上的女装系列则跳到了另一个极端：颜色鲜艳、廓形饱满。秀场陈设简单，只铺着一条白色地毯，两旁点缀着一些石头，模拟山峰。</p><p>在接受 <em>WWD</em> 采访时，JW Anderson 强调时尚必须不断演化，“我希望把噪音关在门外，把注意力集中在衣服、时尚、风格上，尤其是英式质感的材料”。设计师本季对针织的使用别处心裁，一些尺寸夸张、印有佩斯利花纹，另一些则和紧身连衣裙搭配起来，在宽边腰带上堆出松弛的形状。设计师说他喜欢褶皱不循规蹈矩的样子，“一种笨拙的优雅”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144321PetcLzIRyl0oGU64.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144315rbQeafXhxP1I3cl4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144315QEyrMmSeJUTGBCH2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191443156G981Bk57g40uxYf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191443160XjzHOIyZMGbtVPK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144320zcop5r41GtlfdV9U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144320YwpE14IebKgyJDRf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144320t7OPBbxCzTflAvIr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191443210eYu3t2XchUBNlkp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144321FMYreZXVQfD9d0KO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191443212C5fdISupvXOcmUz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144321TlGW49AUmJEOVSwK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191443226zWvPAK38EGi0b4j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144322aefsOHAnbXDKGr9k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144322sDE39R2Hd4hILcvq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144646NxrS1stGdbXa0v8u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/london/vivienne-westwood/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivienne Westwood 2019 秋冬：</a></strong><br></p><p>Vivienne Westwood 的秀场选在了威斯敏斯特的一间由教堂改造后的古典音乐厅里。秀场成了表达政治观点的地方，载体是表演者和服装。Rose McGowan、Camilla Rutherford、Sara Stockbridge 等活动者在现场发表了一系列演讲，主题包括税务不平等、民主、消费主义（“文化的敌人”）、对真相的忽视、气候变化。模特的头饰和身上也印有女权以及反对消费主义相关的标语。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144529qdQiNjH5D7loT6eB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191445298tbyif62mrH9PBaW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144529ifRjXblIGrDBFHWY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144530wZrAbPIem5v821UL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144530s6ujncVaiBzrdFET.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144530l1s34ofGwODPuE6h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144531F8pZuWQz76G5ndxc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144531M0EJP85pAmQcNFTL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144531N5RFXA3OxCvwtiT6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144532rSMR4C2o0LF8mTPE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191445318J7zWTF9bHGdos6v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191445328EgnyH5rOMBzP6Z0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144533APajrcMSX7gKOR8B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191445345KbHw60xd2esaSXR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144538E8F7f32UINmAMW5w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144538DEiO0RT975dtXyr8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144532NsWqPHOfu8CgmBQ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144539iTx3G1VsrCUNeESL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144539mUanoc0sCrPx9T7L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219144540wTnJLkZaN7d1yiQg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/london/wales-bonner/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wales Bonner 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>年轻设计师 Grace Wales Bonner 自 2015 年从伦敦中央圣马丁毕业后就一直是时尚圈的宠儿，以她对于非洲身份认同的探索和出色的剪裁著称，2016 年曾获得&nbsp;LVMH 年轻设计师大奖。</p><p>新系列是该品牌上个月举办的展览“Time for New Dreams”的延伸。设计师说展览当时使用的背景音乐是由美国第一所黑人大学 Howard University 校合唱团演唱，这令她联想到典型的美式大学制服，并试图把最典型的美式高校着装与“西非和加勒比的记忆”相融合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191450165CM2TYIOdKjp70vl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145013t4HsVCTYqiMyZmwg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145013zhxEZw9m2aRyT4Gs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145013d5Mna1YXr6l3BkRy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145014uZUd9PbvGk057Ijo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145014i0Ox9ErsICZd2cN3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145014ZiJvPQOeC0gUkbyE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191450140B41YRDuaLybWMQ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145014gILKV89GvuDBW6ki.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145014HXW3I0ULKuhqwEYV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145015Uzmh02QT3r7oL5F4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902191451217fwDsVeU3ua4AzPK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145422Njd1YyxSkX4J7Pi9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145411PZwlWfNI2jDTaM4p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145016gb4qvJeoDSKCYhnl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/london/kiko-kostadinov/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kiko Kostadinov 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>这是毕业于中央圣马丁的澳大利亚双胞胎姐妹 Deanna 和 Laura Fanning 执掌 Kiko Kostadinov 女装线后呈现的第二个系列。鞋履中包括了两位设计师与 Asics 和 Camper 的联名。</p><p>你可以从该系列中看到材料、色彩、质感和廓形的多方面冲突。设计师试图结合上世纪 70 年代的波兰电影以及 20 世纪初墨西哥女抢匪（bandidas）的形象，制造出一种不同的运动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145615p0HrPD1et8EoBaXA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190219145609ATNaubkIyL7t8l60.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-for